    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or a parts donor. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and widespread clear coat failure. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission requires immediate attention; it is not currently in roadworthy condition and will need to be towed.",
